<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  </head>
  <body style="background: #eeeeee; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
  	<div style="background: #fefefe; width: 70%; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 2rem">
      <div style="padding: 20px;" align="center">
        <a href="https://www.spritle.com">
          <img src="https://www.linkpicture.com/q/spritle_logo.png" style="width: 25%;">
        </a>
        <img src="https://www.linkpicture.com/q/spritle_quote.jpg" style="width: 100%; margin: 2rem 0 2rem 0;">
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 0 20px; font-size: 14px;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #666666;">Hi <%= @user_data['name'] %>!</h3>
        <p style="color: #333333;">
          Greetings from Spritle!
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333;">
          Thanks for being a part of our Freshers Drive. You have been successfully registered for Spritle Online Test. You can take up the test anytime but the time limit would be 60 mins. Once you login using the provided credentials the test will begin.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333;">
          Please find your login credentials below.<br>
          <b style="color: #666666;">Email:</b> <%= @user_data['email'] %><br>
          <b style="color: #666666;">Password:</b> <%= @user_data['password'] %>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333;">
          Click <a href='<%= @user_data["test_link"] %>' style="text-decoration: none; color: #0000ff">here<a> to take test.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333;">
          We would like you to kindly check the mail for the aptitude test status.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 20px; font-size: 14px;">
        <p style="color: #333333;">
          <b style="color: #666666;">Thanks and Regards,</b><br>
          Spritle Hiring Team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
